  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \n  \nBookmarkDragHelper is a self-owned class that takes a bookmark drag request and responsible for deleting itself after drag ends. Its constructor takes a raw pointer to WebContents and stores it as a member [1], and the codes can also observe BookmarkModel events [2]."
